in their first joint political action 
more than 500 indians from 20 amazon rain forest tribes have 
gathered in this jungle town to protest planned hydrolectric dams 
that would flood their lands 
sporting greenandyellow feathered headdresses and red and black 
warpaint about 100 warriors from the kayapo tribe ran chanting into 
