the peoples daily the voice of the communist 
party and chinas leading newspaper is trying out a new look in an 
attempt to win back readers by giving them more of the news that 
interests them 
the paper has seen its circulation fall 20 percent a year 
recently currently 4 million papers are printed a day the most of 
