democratic congressional seats the 4th and 6th congressional 
districts eroded the democrats majority in the delegation in the 
senate republicans gained one of floridas seats when connie mack 
defeated democratic rep buddy mackay to replace the retired 
democrat lawton chiles 
grant won his seat after 12term rep don fuqua a democrat 
decided to retire grant won 51 percent of the vote in a 
