ive had time of course in prison to reflect over this and 
the seriousness of it fondling is you know in my mind i was 
thinking it really doesnt hurt anybody but i know now how much it 
does hurt we just must find a way to help the children first and 
of course the molesters also above all the children who really 
dont know what theyre getting into 
