dismisses clarks critics 
he is universally beloved by his students and thats all that 
counts people who disagree with him are meaningless theyre off in 
some kind of ivory tower i dont think they even know what he did 
some might argue that clark has been operating a fascist state 
so what answers freeman what do you think a school is 
its not a democracy you cant teach democracy if you cant catch 
