<TEXT>
the price of public service company of new 
hampshire common stock fell nearly 14 percent tuesday apparently 
because a barrons magazine article said the stock could become 
worthless when the utility emerges from bankruptcy protection 
the opening of new york stock exchange trading in public service 
common stock was delayed 31 minutes tuesday morning because there 
